videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham runs the fast break and finds Carlton Bragg Jr. on the nifty bounce pass for the monster two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Sweet pass for a sweet dunk by the Jayhawks

videos.description: On a Kansas fast break, Kansas State loses track of Pretty Ellis who gets on the receiving end of a Devonte Graham lob for a huge alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Alley-oops are easy with Perry Ellis running the floor
